reviewText: Not as good as the live TV show. Scripted isn't as funny as spontaneous.
Not as fun as I thought it would be, but kind of fun.

I was embarrassed & disappointed with this DVD that I bought for my niece Lisa.......When she recieved it she was so happy, but then she saw it could only be watched in Ireland..........I felt bad over this as she loves Mrs. Browns Boys......so, we are with a DVD that cannot be watched..........
